// Go to the virtual environment created by "myenv"
command:
	source myenv/bin/activate
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Or one can create his own environment. Use instruct file to create one.

If you create a new environment, install dependencies for transformer and torch

Use the commands:

For Transformer:
	pip install transformers

For Torch:
	pip install torch torchvision torchaudio
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
//Now after all this you can execute the program "summary.py"

Parameters of execution: python summary.py doc

-summary.py is the program
-doc is the document to be summarised. (You can give any documnet)
